## Warm Up

Warm Up:run 1/4 mile OR row 250m OR bike 1/2 miles.
3 rounds of: 10 push ups, 10 sit ups, 10 pull ups (or jumping pull ups)

## WOD

WOD 757

### Étudiant

200   air squats for time.

### Avancée

400 air squats for time.

### Traceur

500 air squats for time.

## Post

Post time to comments.

